{"tid":2362334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"先達廣場兩人初步確診 有店舖拉閘　商戶：最怕冇生意","createTime":"2021-01-11T11:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T16:35:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8afaa8a63716ea27d041562f2401b8d474c3f8be","tid":2362334,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:14:59.000Z","msg":"先達廣場職員確診】新冠肺炎第四波疫情反覆，每日都有 30～40 人確診，今日衛生署方面更確認，手機集散地旺角先達廣場有兩人初步確診。傍晚現場所見，雖然有店舖拉閘，但整體人流沒有減少，有商戶就表示，最擔憂是無生意。<br />\n<br />\n在有人初步確診的消息傳出之後，《香港01》科技玩物頻道記者到現場了解。由於近期 iPhone 12 的炒賣潮已過，先達廣場的人流本身就已經較為稀少，縱然有確診消息傳出，但場內人流無太大變化。<br />\n<br />\n記者先後訪問了幾位先達中人，他們在記者到場前已經知悉場內有人確診的消息，然而問及他們對此事最擔心的地方，他們均不約而同地表示憂慮沒生意，其次才對健康風險有擔憂。"},{"pid":"f9e8435c95002f304f1e36b03f1e803bba082303","tid":2362334,"uid":23468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"成個場都湯水魚咁湯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無生意是常識吧"},{"pid":"f1987be1c967eb402d5624f880658322743f61f1","tid":2362334,"uid":186074,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"iPhone12有炒過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62eb2c24b20ebca5a84901b5b4d31b0b32703b6","tid":2362334,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"本身都冇生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a606c26a3c546ac1ac24913e979b540a72918b9d","tid":2362334,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"RAP"},{"pid":"13be6271c35384c3d42c08c25bf92d913e3471c8","tid":2362334,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62eb2c24b20ebca5a84901b5b4d31b0b32703b6","tid":2362334,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"本身都冇生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:26:38.000Z